### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###                      CREATE POST
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create post (with image and hashtags)
### POST /posts
### Requires: JWT auth cookie
### Body: multipart/form-data
###   - content: string (optional)
###   - hashtags: JSON array (optional)
###   - image: file (optional, max 5MB)
### Returns: Created post
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

This is my new post with an image!
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="hashtags"

["Technology", "Programming", "NestJS"]
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./photo.jpg
--boundary123--

